.TH atomsk 1 LOCAL

.SH NAME
atomsk - Atom/Molecule/Material Software Kit

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B atomsk

.B atomsk <inputfile> <outputfile>

.B atomsk <inputfile> <format>

.B atomsk <inputfile> <format> <options...>

.B atomsk [--mode] <inputfile> <outputfile> [-options] [formats]

.SH AVAILABILITY
Atomsk is intended to run in UNIX/Linux and Microsoft(R) Windows(R) environments.

.SH DESCRIPTION
Atomsk is a command-line program intended to read many types of atomic position files, and convert them to many other formats. A list of supported formats is given below. Additionnaly, atomsk can also perform some simple transformations of atomic positions (thanks to the so-called options).

.SH SUPPORTED FILE FORMATS
.SH Input:
.TP
.B atsk
Specific atomsk binary format.
.TP
